  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study comprises of giving IVIG to half of the septic VLBW preterm neonates along with ongoing
      antibiotics and placebo to the other half. The immunoglobulin will be given for 3 days and
      neonates will be monitored for the results. The data will be analysed on the basis of blood
      culture results and outcome of the patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
