  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Preterm

          -  Very low birth weight baby: birth weight 1-1.5 kg

          -  Both inside and outside delivered babies

          -  Gender: males and females

          -  Probable severe sepsis (septic score)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Extremely low birth weight babies: &lt; 1 kg

          -  Babies &gt;1.5 kg birth weight

          -  Babies born with congenital malformations

          -  Full term babies

          -  IUGR babies

          -  Child with no signs of sepsis

          -  HBsAg Positive

          -  HIV Positive
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
